ing: 1 (29 ounce) can baked beans with pork
des: "You could almost say that these baked beans with a kick have been double-baked!"
ins:
Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).
In a casserole dish, combine beans, brown sugar, ketchup, and Worcestershire sauce.
Bake, covered, for 45 minutes or until bubbly.
